      <short value="Name of character encoding scheme in which this value is encoded."/>
      <definition value="Name of character encoding scheme in which this value is encoded. Coded from openEHR Code Set  character sets . Unicode is the default assumption in openEHR, with UTF-8 being the assumed encoding. This attribute allows for variations from these assumptions."/>
      <min value="0"/>
      <max value="1"/>
